flowchart TD
  A[Task running] --> B{Session idle/stable?}
  B -- No --> C[Continue polling]
  C --> A
  B -- Yes --> D{Has valid output + no incomplete todo?}
  D -- No --> C
  D -- Yes --> E[Complete task + release concurrency]
  E --> F[Notify parent session]
  A --> G{Error / timeout / session deleted?}
  G -- Yes --> H[Interrupt or cancel task]
  H --> I[Abort session + release concurrency]
  I --> F
